OL,4,CSport is 'marking its own homework' on
OL,5,Cathletes' brain injuries, say MPs
OL,6, Sport has been allowed to "mark its own
OL,7, homework" on reducing the risks of
OL,8, brain injury, an MPs' inquiry says.
OL,10,FIts report calls for a standard
OL,11,Fdefinition of concussion that all
OL,12,Fsports must use, and a paid medical
OL,13,Fofficer at every major sporting event.
OL,15,FIt comes as the first study to scan
OL,16,Felite rugby players' brains suggests
OL,17,Fone in four could be at risk of small
OL,18,Fabnormalities.
OL,20,FBut the long-term effects on brain
OL,21,Fhealth are not clear, researchers say.
